com.sun.identity.saml.assertion
Class Attribute

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.identity.saml.assertion.AttributeDesignator
      com.sun.identity.saml.assertion.Attribute
public class Attribute
extends AttributeDesignator

The element specifies an attribute of the assertion subject. The element is an extension of the element that allows the attribute value to be specified.
